OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy at
OL,6,Ffirst this evening with spells of
OL,7,Frain. Clearer intervals will develop
OL,8,Ffrom the west overnight, though the
OL,9,Ffar southeast may stay cloudy until
OL,10,Fdawn. Winds generally light, with
OL,11,Ftemperatures turning chilly where
OL,12,Fskies clear.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FDry and bright through the
OL,15,Fmorning, then becoming mostly cloudy
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon with a few
OL,17,Fshowers moving across the area.
OL,18,FClearer spells overnight may lead to a
OL,19,Fpatchy frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
